{"tid":1295630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察便服日？","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:02:33.000Z","uid":257855,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8df1ca50656ac310bd68504ee527a8e140fa19b","tid":1295630,"uid":257855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NNHBW2Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNNHBW2Q.png&h=9fa264b1&s={SIZE}\" />一個頭盔，便服，又無帶委任證，其實我地求其搵一個人出去做都得啦，佢地琴晚搞緊警察便服日？"},{"pid":"c0165575c55acf7a063519b632c51a1847048766","tid":1295630,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:40:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫手推上熱門<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［重要］區議會選舉招募各路人馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295057</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，光復行動冇可能每日都做<br />\n好似屯門公園搞到今日咁烏煙瘴氣區議員責無旁貸<br />\n要清洗屯門公園始終要由根源做起<br />\n所以除左投立法會外<br />\n都請記得投票區議會踢走自動當選建制派<br />\n<br />\n唔好再俾建制派霸哂啲議席<br />\n就算唔係參選都可以做提名人，義工，助選團<br />\n行出第一步拒絕自動當選！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總台TG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDistrictCouncil2019&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=1a14972f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019</a><br />\n</span></span><br />\n登記左做選民既全部入group<br />\n急需大量提名人，義工助選團，Design等職位<br />\n入group後右下角Discuss入公頻搵各區admin<br />\n<br />\n要對抗黑警濫權一定要有議員抗衡<br />\n否則只會一直任人魚肉"},{"pid":"0115fb683ff48e96b46dfc59dd3792228318938e","tid":1295630,"uid":270824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:42:14.000Z","msg":"媽阿 好柒 <br />\n隔離白衫心諗今次仆街拉，比你個便服傻仔咁講野"},{"pid":"b8f770a4a4cc2f425cd6bdc8615a1b645515077c","tid":1295630,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislik